&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;Develop and improve manufacturing processes and tooling for composite parts&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;Work with production teams to ensure manufacturability and suggest improvements.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;Train production staff&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;new processes and techniques.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;Providing&amp;nbsp;manufacturing support to&amp;nbsp;design throughout conceptual, preliminary,&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;detailed design phases,&amp;nbsp;to include&amp;nbsp;validation,&amp;nbsp;customer approval, manufacturing, and operational service.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
