&lt;li&gt;Experience with GCP preferred (AWS or comparable cloud platforms acceptable). Palantir Foundry is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to lead technical teams and present architectures to executive audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with AI Agent frameworks (LangGraph, ADK) and classical ML is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; hybrid in Herndon, VA (3 days office min)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
