&lt;li&gt;Generate and maintain requirements aligned with &lt;strong&gt;customer, regulatory, and certification needs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure &lt;strong&gt;bidirectional traceability&lt;/strong&gt; between requirements, verification methods, and compliance evidence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage requirements within an &lt;strong&gt;ALM environment&lt;/strong&gt; (e.g., Polarion)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide critical design feedback related to &lt;strong&gt;safety, requirements completeness, and verification readiness&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
