&lt;h2&gt;Business Development&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement the sales strategy in the field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the sale of technical service offerings, from prospecting to contract negotiation and signature&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure client satisfaction with a focus on retaining existing accounts and building long-term, profitable partnerships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be accountable for the profitability and growth of your business portfolio&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Talent Acquisition &amp;amp; Management&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify engineering profiles in collaboration with the dedicated recruitment team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct interviews and ensure the successful onboarding of your new hires&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support consultants in building their career paths within the Group&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;PROFILE SOUGHT&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum bachelor’s degree in engineering or business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 3+ years of successful experience in industry, services, or engineering-related fields&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An entrepreneurial spirit with the ambition to quickly grow into leadership positions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Natural leadership skills and the ability to build strong relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Results-oriented with a rigorous and structured approach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;WHY JOIN US?&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Becoming a Business Manager means joining a path of excellence leading to senior leadership roles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At ALTEN USA, we value performance and encourage talent to emerge through:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A structured career path with clear progression within the Group&lt;/li&gt;
